{"tid":491372,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"其實騰訊跌係因為我買左","createTime":"2017-12-06T12:47:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-06T13:02:00.000Z","uid":146999,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ace9d68b60bf0cae9d9858fdbc18920441c86db0","tid":491372,"uid":146999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T12:47:10.000Z","msg":"我係典型散戶，高追殺跌樣樣齊，我一入市通常就散水。<br />\n上年見騰訊係咁升，係年尾見佢由高位220跌到200就入左貨，190止蝕，最後跌到落180。（18x入番）<br />\n6月9號去買美股，主要係科技股，當日立即爆發小型股災，主要都係集中係科技股。隻NVDA日日爆升，到我買既當日都升緊唔小，點知我一買（大概11點），由當時既最高位一直跌到落全日低位收市，高低點相差兩成左右，好入肉。<br />\n之前買既700，我係240就放左。係佢270個時，我同朋友講話貴。 點知呢期見佢日日係咁升，見周街都咁賺錢，令到我一直都好想買番佢食下條水，最尾係4xx買。<br />\n<br />\n我一直都知自己好黑仔，買咩股票前都會同身邊朋友單聲。我當時既想法係：無理由要我睇住全世界係咁賺錢，我都要玩埋一份，要蝕錢就一齊蝕。<br />\n<br />\n點知真係蝕錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過唔怕因爲其他人都賺唔到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：得一手700正股"},{"pid":"c55c3f7f9e748490b5d5670e200aee376d17f416","tid":491372,"uid":1374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T12:51:18.000Z","msg":"睇得自己咁重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfa442afe391e92dc602c412e38fb864559f7838","tid":491372,"uid":22507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T12:52:50.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 終於搵到你<br />\n就係你搞到我蝕左60萬"},{"pid":"aeb63c911d13e6b510eac2b0f7443681dcc1c04b","tid":491372,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T12:54:21.000Z","msg":"一手<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb57d3765307c251dd6bd25fe58bd5ee87b2617c","tid":491372,"uid":26971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T12:55:31.000Z","msg":"講咁多 入左熊未？"},{"pid":"4de75b514f0fd439f795d16ccd29c372639747f8","tid":491372,"uid":126329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T12:55:50.000Z","msg":"你邊位?"},{"pid":"15debaef9b9668005d934d0f668eff9c68d1af35","tid":491372,"uid":136727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T12:56:51.000Z","msg":"其實唔關你事，係連燈仔燈姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49e9b2faa768e3165874e61056a0415bc372ee20","tid":491372,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T12:58:45.000Z","msg":"同我一鳩樣,唔知係咪真係黑仔成咁<br />\n升果陣冇買,買果就開始走下坡"},{"pid":"a7f36b6b72b575030a6c46321dc3b1f864ea91b3","tid":491372,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T12:59:21.000Z","msg":"想知樓主諗住幾時放 ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b2c7ecc86495cd3f8611b842fc6f439321088a1","tid":491372,"uid":57308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T12:59:39.000Z","msg":"唔係你燈，係你只係一個俾大戶收割既傻鳩姐<br />\n唔好諗到自己咁重要，只係你做晒唔應該做既野<br />\n唔通你買六合彩唔中又話自己燈到人地中頭獎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"492b829e8b392e8d2e59e0343221dbf7c2046d23","tid":491372,"uid":63588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T13:02:00.000Z","msg":"你邊位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我淨係知書包415入左"}]}